    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231820/extras/84d8fdef77308112deb1c0287551109d.avif?t=1671691502\" width=800 height=800 /></span><br><br><strong>intimate Swordplay<strong><br>one of my main focuses in this game is to create a engaging close quarters combat system, no fancy cartwheel triple jumps that send your character 10 feet in the air or flashy 5 button combos, just close intimate swordplay. finding gaps in your opponents defenses before they find find a gap in yours. maneuver around shields, parry and deflect attack, and counter when you find an opening or create one yourself.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231820/extras/7caa631ab51961620ecffb6fb885551d.poster.avif?t=1671691502\" width=800 height=672 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231820/extras/7caa631ab51961620ecffb6fb885551d.webm?t=1671691502\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231820/extras/7caa631ab51961620ecffb6fb885551d.mp4?t=1671691502\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>intercontinental Platformer/rpg<strong><br>unlike most action-platformers and metroidvanias this game has a expansive RPG-like overworld with caves, forests, mountains, towns and dungeons with secrets, oddities and danger everywhere you go.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231820/extras/e11dbd12aad2782e3d667c50b0bf34ea.gif?t=1671691502\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231820/extras/e11dbd12aad2782e3d667c50b0bf34ea.poster.avif?t=1671691502\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><br><br><strong>A Living World Under Duress</strong><br>Im very passionate about making a world feel like a living breathing space, where every NPC, home, &amp; village feels like a small part of a larger living, breathing world. there are secrets hidden behind every corner, people with routines and relationships, places with cultural beliefs and histories.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231820/extras/9809ef54f047c4b86e048e4075817075.webp?t=1671691502\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231820/extras/9809ef54f047c4b86e048e4075817075.poster.avif?t=1671691502\" class=\"bb_img\" width=800 height=889 /></picture></span></strong></strong></strong></strong>",
